metadata.name: New Era - The Merge
metadata.description:
A collaboration between 

Clat ( 3D Artist )
Daniele Cruciani ( Photographer )
W3N ( Digital Artist )

The Ethereum Merge marks one of the most important moments in crypto history.
This artwork is an homage to all the developers that made it possible, we are now beginning to explore a new era for crypto and cryptoart.
